<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Qmarshal - Engineering Urban Flow</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Qmarshal is a reliable platform that simplifies urban mobility through real-time passenger tracking and quick pickup requests.">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div id="three-canvas-container"></div>

    <div id="preloader">
        <div class="loader-visual"></div>
        <p>Initializing Qmarshal Network...</p>
    </div>

    <header id="main-header" class="container">
        <div class="logo">Qmarshal</div>
    </header>

    <main id="scroll-container">

        <section id="hero" class="scroll-section full-height">
            <div class="content-layer text-center">
                <h1 class="main-headline">Re-Engineering<br>Urban <span class="highlight-blue">Mobility</span>.</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Track, request, and ride — all in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-indicator">
                <span>Scroll Down</span>
                <div class="arrow">↓</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="network" class="scroll-section content-section">
            <div class="content-layer text-content">
                <h2 class="section-title">Reliable <span class="highlight-magenta">Connections</span></h2>
                <p>Qmarshal brings passengers and drivers together with speed and reliability. Every ride request is handled in real time for faster pickups and smoother trips.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-location-arrow"></i> Real-Time Passenger Tracking</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-taxi"></i> Quick and Simple Ride Requests</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-route"></i> Smarter Route Coordination</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="experience" class="scroll-section content-section">
            <div class="content-layer text-content text-right">
                <h2 class="section-title">Seamless <span class="highlight-blue">Experience</span></h2>
                <p>From booking to drop-off, Qmarshal makes it easy. The app is designed for both riders and drivers, making every interaction smooth and efficient.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Easy-To-Use Interface</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-bell"></i> Instant Notifications</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Ride Confirmation in Seconds</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="trust" class="scroll-section content-section">
            <div class="content-layer text-content">
                <h2 class="section-title">Built on <span class="highlight-magenta">Trust</span></h2>
                <p>Qmarshal focuses on reliability. With clear trip tracking and verified users, every ride is safer and more dependable.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i> Verified Drivers</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Live Trip Updates</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Support When You Need It</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="download" class="scroll-section full-height final-cta">
            <div class="content-layer text-center">
                <h2 class="cta-headline">Experience <span class="highlight-magenta">Qmarshal</span>.</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Download now and discover a better way to move through your city.</p>
                <div class="download-buttons">
                    <a href="assets/app/Qmarshal_App.zip" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg download-button" download>
                        <i class="fas fa-download me-2"></i> Direct Download
                    </a>
                </div>
                <p class="disclaimer mt-3"><small>(App Store / Play Store version coming soon.)</small></p>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer id="main-footer">
        &copy; <span id="current-year"></span> Qmarshal Technologies.
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="js/three-scene.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Simple script to set the current year in the footer
        document.getElementById('current-year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>

</body>
</html>